3ECopilot's%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reviews%20%E2%80%94%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20Microsoft%20%E2%80%94%20indicate%20that%20the%20new%20product%20is%20struggling%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20hype.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20single%20measurement%20of%20Copilot's%20performance%2C%20given%20the%20wide%20array%20of%20features%20it%20seeks%20to%20provide%2C%20many%20customers%20appear%20to%20be%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20AI%20tool%2C%20complaining%20that%20it%20is%20ineffective%2C%20costly%2C%20and%20not%20secure.%20In%20October%2C%20when%20the%20management%20consultancy%20Gartner%20published%20a%20survey%20of%20123%20IT%20leaders%2C%20only%20four%20said%20Copilot%20provided%20significant%20value%20to%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Microsoft's%20own%20employees%20and%20executives%20are%20privately%20concerned%20that%20Copilot%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20ambitions.%20To%20assess%20the%20tool's%20rollout%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20central%20role%20it%20plays%20in%20Microsoft's%20historic%2C%20all-out%20investment%20in%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed%20internal%20emails%20and%20pay%20spreadsheets%2C%20spoke%20with%20customers%20and%20competitors%2C%20and%20interviewed%2015%20current%20and%20former%20Microsoft%20insiders%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20requested%20anonymity%20to%20speak%20freely%20about%20internal%20matters.%20Many%20of%20those%20charged%20with%20building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-marc-benioff-criticized-microsoft-copilot-ai-agents-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20say%20they%20harbor%20doubts%20about%20what%20it%20will%20ultimately%20achieve.%20Others%20in%20the%20company%20express%20serious%20doubts%20about%20Microsoft's%20immense%20investment%20in%20a%20technology%20that%20they%20see%20as%20unproven%20%E2%80%94%20and%20potentially%20unprofitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20feel%20like%20I'm%20livi