fore%20wading%20into%20crypto.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBy%20not%20following%20my%20friends'%20advice%2C%20I%20avoided%20a%20lot%20of%20losses%20on%20things%20like%20meme%20coins.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-buy-stock%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20I%20made%20a%20promise%20to%20myself%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20give%20in%20to%20peer%20pressure%20from%20friends%2C%20social%20media%2C%20or%20commentary%20in%20the%20news.%20I%20had%20spent%20years%20making%20mistakes%20with%20my%20money%2C%20and%20after%20working%20hard%20to%20clean%20up%20my%20finances%20and%20stick%20to%20a%20strict%20budget%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20ease%20into%20the%20world%20of%20investing%20by%20researching%20and%20strategizing%20first.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20didn't%20rush%20to%20invest%20in%20every%20new%20crypto%20of%20the%20week%2C%20I%20was%20not%20only%20able%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20more%20holistic%20goals%2C%20like%20retirement%20savings%2C%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-passive-income-strategies-build-wealth-earning-money-2023-9%5C%22%3Epassive%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20managing%20my%20spending%2C%20but%20I%20also%20believe%20I%20really%20benefited%20from%20ignoring%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20ways%20I%20came%20out%20as%20a%20winner%20by%20ignoring%20these%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20friends%20rushed%20to%20buy%20meme%20coins%20%E2%80%94%20like%20dogecoin%20or%20shiba%20inu%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20when%20they%20went%20viral%20in%20both%20the%20news%20and%20on%20crypto%20forums%20in%202020.%20Some%20made%20short-term%20profits%20by%20buying%20the%20coins%20at%20a%20low%20price%20and%20selling%20them%20as%20the%20price%20skyrocketed%2C%20but%20others%20held%20on%20too%20long%20and%20ended%20up%20losing%20quite%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20meme%20coins%20seemed%20to%20be%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20viral%20attention%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20give%20in%20to%20the%20hype%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20I%20could%20have%20made%20a%20profit.%20Since%20I'm%20new%20to%20this%2C%20I%20couldn't%20justify%20the%20risk%20of%20buying%20these%20meme%20coins%20since%20I%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20them%20or%20what%20their%20purpose%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20had%20listened%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20bought%20dogecoin%20when%20they%20did%2C%20I%20would%20have%20lost%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20I%20bought%20bitcoin%20during%20a%20dip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20friends%20bought%20more%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-cryptocurrency%5C%22%3Ecryptocurrencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20their%20all-time%20highs.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20buy%20bitcoin%20when%20it%20shot%20up%20in%20value%20and%20was%20worth%20over%20%2460%2C000%20per%20coin%20in%20April.%20After%20doing%20some%20research%20and%20trusting%20my%20gut%2C%20though%2C%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20buy%20it%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20invested%C2%A0when%20bitcoin%20fell%20to%20around%20%2440%2C000%20per%20coin.%20As%20a%20rookie%20investor%2C%20I%20try%20to%20always%20remember%20to%20buy%20during%20a%20dip%20and%20not%20when%20prices%20are%20skyrocketing%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20price%20is%20only%20going%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20I%20invested%20in%20multiple%20coins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20friends%20have%20a%20strategy%20of%20going%20all%20in%20on%20one%20cryptocurrency.%20I%20decided%20that%20since%20there's%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20news%2C%20changes%2C%20and%20growth%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%20space%2C%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20follow%20their%20strategy.%20Instead%2C%20I%20would%20hold%20anywhere%20between%20three%20to%20five%20coins%20at%20once%20based%20on%20what%20I%20felt%20would%20increase%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20hard%20to%20compare%20who%20has%20the%20better%20strategy%20because%20we're%20all%20approaching%20this%20with%20a%20long-term%20lens%2C%20I%20believe%20this%20helps%20me%20manage%20risk%20and%20it%20eases%20my%20anxiety%20as%20an%20investor.%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20to%20micromanage%20my%20crypto%20portfolio%20daily%20in%20fear%20of%20suffering%20major%20losses%20if%20one%20coin%20takes%20a%20dive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20I%20made%20gains%20elsewhere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20friends%20pulled%20most%20of%20their%20cash%20out%20of%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20invested%20it%20in%20crypto%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20my%20investments%20diversified%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fmutual-funds%5C%22%3Emutual%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20other%20investments.%20This%20helped%20me%20not%20only%20manage%20risk%2C%20but%20also%20benefit%20from%20certain%20stocks%20hitting%20all-time%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20listened%20to%20my%20friends%2C%20I'd%20only%20be%20able%20to%20make%20gains%20from%20buying%20cryptocurrency.%20That's%20not%20something%20I%20want%20to%20rely%20on%2C%20as%20I%20am%20an%20investor%20who%20is%20aiming%20to%20have%20a%20more%20holistic%20financial%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20I%20watched%20and%20learned%20from%20other%20people's%20mistakes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20learn%20a%20lot%20by%20watching%20my%20friends%20who%20started%20earlier%20than%20I%20did.%20Some%20of%20my%20friends%20have%20been%20buying%20crypto%20for%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20in%20the%20middle%20of%202020%2C%20so%20I%20was%20able%20to%20ask%20them%20questions%2C%20view%20their%20portfolios%2C%20and%20learn%20from%20their%20mistakes%2C%20like%20buying%20too%20high%2C%20selling%20too%20quickly%2C%20or%20putting%20too%20much%20cash%20into%20meme%20stocks%20that%20crashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20November%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenefited-from-ignoring-cryptocurrency-fads-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731705301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f402a0589aff80028ab74b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenefited-from-ignoring-cryptocurrency-fads-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20of%20my%20friends%20got%20on%20the%20bandwagon%20when%20cryptocurrency%20trading%20exploded%20in%202020%2C%20but%20I%20paused.%20I%20don't%20regret%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenefited-from-ignoring-cryptocurrency-fads-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Accused%20of%20fund%20misuse%2C%20Karnataka%20to%20make%20temple%20audit%20reports%20public%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731705300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115344845%2Cimgsize-1614690.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faccused-of-fund-misuse-karnataka-to-make-temple-audit-reports-public%2Farticleshow%2F115344796.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20will%20publicly%20disclose%20audit%20reports%20of%20major%20temples%20(A%20and%20B%20category)%20under%20its%20endowment%20department.%20This%20decision%20aims%20to%20address%20allegations%20by%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20regarding%20