5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20were%20imposed%20under%20stage%20III%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%2C%20or%20GRAP%2C%20announced%20by%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20quality%20index%20in%20Delhi%20was%20411%20(severe)%20at%209%20am%20on%20Friday%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data.%20However%2C%20with%20wind%20speed%20picking%20up%2C%20the%20average%2024-hour%20AQI%20at%204%20pm%20came%20down%20to%20396%2C%20still%20in%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20the%20situation%20will%20improve%20further%20with%20higher%20wind%20speed%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Atishi%20announced%20staggered%20timings%20for%20government%20offices%20in%20the%20city%20to%20ease%20traffic%20congestion%20given%20the%20pollution%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20schedule%20announced%20by%20her%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20central%20government%20offices%20will%20operate%20from%209%20am%20to%205.30%20pm%2C%20Delhi%20government%20offices%20from%2010%20am%20to%206.30%20pm%2C%20and%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20offices%20from%208.30%20am%20to%205%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20LG%20V%20K%20Saxena%20issued%20a%20note%20approving%20the%20staggered%20government%20office%20timings%20till%20February%202025%2C%20expressing%20dissatisfaction%20that%20a%20measure%20that%20should%20have%20been%20in%20place%20as%20a%20pre-emptive%20step%20was%20implemented%20with%20a%20delay%20of%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20would%20ensure%20strict%20enforcement%20of%20other%20measures%20discussed%20in%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(DDMA)%20on%20pollution%20control%20on%20October%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERai%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20announced%20various%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20air%20quality%20has%20been%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category%20for%20the%20last%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20run%20106%20shuttle%20buses%20and%20the%20Metro%20trains%20will%20make%2060%20extra%20trips%20daily%20to%20promote%20public%20transport.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20private%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%20while%20necessary%20government%20construction%20works%20will%20continue%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20officials%20living%20across%20the%20city%20will%20be%20transported%20in%2040%20dedicated%20shuttle%20buses%20to%20discourage%20the%20use%20of%20private%20vehicles%20by%20them%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20BS%20III%20petrol%20and%20BS%20IV%20diesel%20vehicles%20were%20banned%20from%20roads%20with%20violations%20inviting%20a%20penalty%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20Diesel%20and%20petrol%20inter-state%20buses%20from%20the%20NCR%20cities%20to%20Delhi%20are%20also%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transport%20department%20has%20deployed%2084%20teams%2C%20with%20an%20additional%20280%20personnel%20for%20catching%20violators%2C%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECity%20schools%20for%20Classes%20up%20to%205%20will%20shift%20to%20online%20mode%20after%20the%20weekend.%20Principals%20and%20teachers%20of%20several%20private%20schools%20said%20they%20were%20using%20apps%20and%20smart%20boards%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahesh%20Palawat%20of%20Skymet%20Weather%20Services%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20air%20quality%20improved%20on%20Friday%20due%20to%20wind%20speeds%20of%208%20to%2012%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20AQI%20will%20remain%20in%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category%20on%20Saturday%2C%20it%20will%20improve%20comparatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20Delhi's%2039%20monitoring%20stations%2C%2018%20reported%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category%2C%20down%20from%2027%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20according%20to%20Sameer%20app%2C%20which%20provides%20hourly%20updates%20of%20the%20national%20AQI%20published%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stations%20include%20Alipur%2C%20Anand%20Vihar%2C%20Ashok%20Vihar%2C%20Aya%20Nagar%2C%20Bawana%2C%20DTU%2C%20Dwarka%20Sector%208%2C%20IGI%20Airport%2C%20Jahangirpuri%2C%20Mundka%2C%20Narela%2C%20Nehru%20Nagar%2C%20Patparganj%20and%20Punjabi%20Bagh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centre's%20Decision%20Support%20System%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%2C%20stubble%20burning%20was%20the%20highest%20contributor%20to%20Delhi's%20pollution%20on%20Thursday%2C%20accounting%20for%20approximately%2033.3%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicular%20emissions%20contributed%20an%20estimated%2011.9%20per%20cent%20to%20Delhi's%20pollution%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prominent%20pollutant%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CPCB%2C%20was%20PM2.5%2C%20which%20are%20fine%20particles%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%202.5%20micrometres%20or%20less%2C%20about%20the%20width%20of%20a%20human%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20particles%20are%20so%20small%20that%20they%20can%20penetrate%20deep%20into%20the%20lungs%20and%20even%20enter%20the%20bloodstream%2C%20posing%20significant%20health%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731703980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F2jmidmcg_delhi-pollution_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-pollution-curbs-staggered-timings-for-delhi-government-offices-7029845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20government%20has%20banned%20private%20BS%20III%20petrol%20and%20BS%20IV%20diesel%20vehicles%2C%2