f%20the%20school%20and%20smoked%20cigarettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20long%20before%20I%20had%20my%20first%20taste%20of%20beer.%20Then%20it%20was%20whiskey%2C%20vodka%2C%20and%20gin%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20we%20could%20get%20our%20hands%20on%20as%20young%20teens.%20We'd%20stand%20outside%20the%20liquor%20store%20and%20ask%20an%20adult%20to%20buy%20bottles%20for%20us.%20Or%20the%20store%20owners%20would%20just%20sell%20it%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20high%20school%2C%20I'd%20drink%20at%20parties%20and%20friends'%20houses.%20My%20parents%20found%20out%20and%20would%20ground%20me.%20But%20I'd%20find%20a%20way%20to%20drink%20in%20secret%20in%20my%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2018%2C%20they%20told%20me%20to%20either%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20or%20go%20to%20rehab.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrew-barrymore-teen-drug-rehab-center-mothers-day-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThey%20paid%20for%20a%20rehab%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Florida.%20I%20had%20one%20relapse%20but%20stayed%20sober%20for%20over%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22135ac0e4-f076-4b38-91d2-83c663dbdf6a%5C%22%3EI%20was%20an%20obnoxious%20person%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%20the%20mid-90s%2C%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20died%20from%20a%20heart%20attack.%20He%20was%20in%20his%2020s.%20I%20went%20to%20his%20funeral%20and%20met%20up%20with%20my%20old%20friends%20that%20I%20used%20to%20drink%20with.%20I%20couldn't%20resist%20the%20temptation%20and%20fell%20back%20into%20bad%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20married%20my%20wife%2C%20Suzanna%2C%20in%202002.%20She%20meant%20everything%20to%20me.%20But%20on%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-go-on-honeymoon-before-getting-engaged-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoneymoon%20in%20Jamaica%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20got%20completely%20blitzed.%20I%20had%20to%20be%20carried%20off%20to%20my%20room.%20She%20was%20embarrassed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20scenes.%20We'd%20go%20to%20parties%20where%20I'd%20get%20drunk%2C%20flirt%20with%20other%20women%2C%20and%20say%20inappropriate%20things.%20I%20was%20an%20obnoxious%2C%20horrible%20husband%20who'd%20yell%20at%20Suzanna%20and%20then%20blackout.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20I%20couldn't%20remember%20a%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20got%20progressively%20worse.%20I%20started%20drinking%20during%20my%20workday.%20The%20pandemic%20meant%20I%20was%20working%20from%20home%2C%20which%20made%20it%20harder.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-own-alcohol-at-home-cocktail-recipes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20brewed%20my%20own%20beer%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20basement%2C%20where%20I'd%20hang%20out%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202021%2C%20our%20marriage%20was%20so%20rocky%20that%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20divorced.%20We%20each%20spent%20%2410%2C000%20on%20lawyers%2C%20but%20somehow%2C%20Suzanna%2C%20now%2051%2C%20forgave%20me.%20We%20worked%20hard%20on%20our%20marriage%20and%20called%20off%20the%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20middle-aged%20man%20on%20a%20dock%20holding%20up%20a%20fish%20he%20just%20caught.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67379802ede4eeae3927ee23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Horton%20is%20living%20life%20to%20the%20full%20after%20conquering%20his%20addiction%20to%20alcohol.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jeff%20Horton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20summer%2C%20I%20blacked%20out%20once%20again.%20It%20frightened%20me%20so%20much%20that%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20get%20ahold%20of%20myself.%20I%20was%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20losing%20my%20job%20or%20dying.%20I'm%205ft%2011in%20and%20weighed%20260%20pounds.%20I'd%20be%20drenched%20in%20sweat%20doing%20simple%20tasks%20like%20picking%20up%20leaves.%20My%20blood%20pressure%20and%20cholesterol%20levels%20were%20dangerously%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20HR%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20my%20company.%20I'd%20worked%20there%20for%2030%20years%2C%20and%20they%20care%20about%20me.%20I%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20take%20a%20monthlong%20leave%20to%20go%20to%20rehab.%20They%20told%20me%20to%20get%20better%20and%20come%20back%20when%20I%20was%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20detoxed%20at%20a%2030-day%20residential%20program%20at%20Mount%20Sinai%20Wellness%20Center%20in%20Dahlonega%2C%20Georgia.%20I%20had%20group%20sessions%20and%20individual%20counseling.%20I%20picked%20up%20the%20tools%20to%20stay%20sober.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22045f0686-5bd3-4e35-ae7f-80ae21e2ca07%5C%22%3EI%20no%20longer%20crave%20alcohol%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20ongoing%20support.%20In%20August%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vivitrol.com%2Falcohol-dependence%3Futm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_campaign%3D2022%2BBranded%26utm_term%3Dvivitrol_exact%26utm_content%3DBrand%2B-%2BExact%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds%26%26gclsrc%3Daw.ds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20doctors%20prescribed%20me%20Vivitrol%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20medication%20that%20helps%20reduce%20alcohol%20dependence.%20They%20explained%20how%20it%20affects%20the%20opioid%20pathways%20to%20the%20brain%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20get%20that%20%26quot%3Bbuzz%26quot%3B%20from%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20me%20not%20want%20to%20drink%20at%20all.%20It%20lost%20its%20appeal%20because%20it%20didn't%20have%20the%20same%20effect%20on%20me.%20I%20told%20Suzanna%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20my%20distilling%20equipment%20in%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20monthly%20intramuscular%20shots%20at%20a%20local%20pharmacy.%20They%20inject%20the%20extended-release%20drug%20between%20my%20buttocks%20and%20hips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20have%20changed%20my%20life.%20I%20have%20no%20inclination%20to%20drink%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-calorie-counting-helped-me-improve-my-relationship-with-food-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20calories%20I've%20saved%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20helped%20me%20lose%2070%20pounds.%20It's%20turned%20my%20metabolism%20around.%20I%20was%20a%2044-inch%20waist%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20a%2034.%20I've%20gone%20from%20an%20XXL%20to%20a%20large.%20I've%20got%20more%20energy%20for%20my%20favorite%20sport%2C%20fishing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuzanna%20and%20Joel%2C%2032%2C%20are%20proud%20of%20me.%20Joel's%20wife%2C%20Harley%2C%20gave%20birth%20to%20our%20beautiful%20grandchild%2C%20Nora%2C%20two%20years%20ago.%20Thank%20God%20she%20has%20never%20seen%20me%20drunk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20never%20will.%20People%20tell%20me%20I'm%20a%20great%2C%20hands-on%20granddad.%20I'm%20very%20happy%20to%20play%20with%20Nora%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20making%20up%20for%20the%20time%20I%20didn't%20spend%20with%20Joel%20when%20he%20was%20young.%20I%20treasure%20every%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20an%20interesting%20story%20to%20share%20with%20Business%20Insider%20about%20making%20a%20life%20change%3F%20Please%20send%20details%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajridley%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ejridley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-sober-lost-seventy-pounds-after-drug-changed-relationship-drink-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731701300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673768bdfa0140cdd563ba1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-sober-lost-seventy-pounds-after-drug-changed-relationship-drink-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeff%20Horton%20was%20not%20