eature%20that%20fuels%20livestream%20sales%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20who%20receive%20the%20gifts%20through%20the%20program%20will%20earn%20%26quot%3Brubies%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20redeemable%20for%20one%20cent%20each%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20its%20announcement%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok's%20LIVE%20Gifts%20feature%20operates%20similarly.%20It%20lets%20app%20users%20purchase%20%26quot%3Bcoins%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20buy%20virtual%20gifts%20of%20monetary%20value%20for%20livestreaming%20creators.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20on%20TikTok%20who%20receive%20the%20gifts%20can%20also%20earn%20%26quot%3Bdiamonds%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.tiktok.com%2Fen%2Flive-gifts-wallet%2Ftiktok-live%2Flive-gifts-on-tiktok%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erewards%20based%20on%20the%20popularity%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20livestream.%20Users%20can%20use%20diamonds%20to%20obtain%20%26quot%3Breward%20payments%26quot%3B%20from%20TikTok%20in%20the%20form%20of%20money%20or%20virtual%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE-commerce%20through%20livestreaming%20platforms%20has%20become%20a%20lucrative%20and%20competitive%20channel%20for%20revenue.%20In%202022%2C%20total%20US%20e-commerce%20sales%20exceeded%20%241%20trillion%2C%20Forbes%20reported.%20Live%20shopping%20accounted%20for%20about%20%2420%20billion%20of%20that.%20Livestream%20e-commerce%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20to%20%2468%20billion%20by%202026%2C%20according%20to%20Statista%2C%20a%20data%20research%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%20has%20dominated%20livestreaming%20e-commerce%20in%20China%20through%20TikTok's%20sister%20app%2C%20Douyin.%20Douyin%20generates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3De54b484532789f314b635c6d0830451432638ce3089beed16d5b0b23d8dfe87c%26postID%3D6736796a12ccc579828c6ef5%26postSlug%3Dyoutube-gifting-feature-tiktok-livestream-e-