llo%3C%2Fem%3E'%20star%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20had%20unforgettable%20moments%20here%20in%20India.%20It's%20like%20a%20second%20home%20to%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20always%20here%20to%20do%20many%20things.%20Often%20for%20weddings...%20we%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20(performances%20for)%20weddings.%20So%20I%20always%20find%20myself%20in%20and%20out%20of%20India.%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20will%20ever%20be%20in%20a%20position%20where%20India%20would%20be%20far%20away%20from%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2051-year-old%20Grammy%20winning%20artiste%20made%20his%20Bollywood%20debut%20by%20singing%20the%20iconic%20'%3Cem%3EChammak%20Challo'%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20'%3Cem%3ECriminal%3C%2Fem%3E'%20songs%20in%20the%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan-starrer%20Ra.One.%20He%20is%20also%20engaged%20in%20philanthropy%20in%20Africa%20and%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3B100%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20willing%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20social%20work%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20hundred%20percent...%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20finding%20the%20best%20potential%20partners%20here.%20But%20I%20would%20love%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20here%20in%20India%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20his%20philanthropic%20work%20such%20as%20the%20solar%20lighting%20project%20(Akon%20Lighting%20Africa)%20in%20Africa%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20carrying%20out%20similar%20work%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20is%20visiting%20the%20northeast%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20the%20trip%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bamazing%26quot%3B%20so%20far.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20I%20am%20visiting%20this%20side%20of%20India.%20It's%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer%20also%20visited%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20linked%20to%20the%20indigenous%20Khasi%20tribe%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMusic%20is%20one%20of%20those%20things%20that%20you%20have%20to%20spread...%20(it)%20also%20speaks%20in%20a%20language%20that%2C%20most%20often%2C%20the%20world%20doesn't%20speak%2C..%20music%2C%20everybody%20understands%20(stands%20for%20the%20language%20of)%20love%2C%20good%20karma%20and%20positive%20energy.%20So%2C%20oftentimes%2C%20if%20you%20do%20music%20with%20positive%20energy%2C%20it%20will%20spread%20quicker%20and%20you%20can%20become%20the%20biggest%20thing%20ever.%20So%20just%20keep%20it%20(your%20music)%20as%20positive%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20message%20to%20all%20his%20fans%2C%20Akon%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20appreciate%20all%20you%20guys%20for%20all%20the%20support%20and%20one%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cherry%20Blossom%20Festival%2C%20which%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20Meghalaya%20government%2C%20is%20being%20held%20on%20Friday%20and%20Saturday.%20With%20impressive%20lineups%2C%20the%20festival%20attracts%20thousands%20of%20music%20enthusiasts%20from%20across%20the%20country%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkon's%20performance%20at%20the%20event%20this%20year%20is%20part%20of%20his%20%26quot%3BSuperfan%20Tour%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20includes%20one%20show%20per%20country%20in%20Asia%20during%20November%20and%20December%2C%20with%20additional%20stops%20in%20as%20many%20as%20eight%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731691500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fv32emfn_akon_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-is-my-second-home-lonely-star-akon-7028753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senegalese-American%20pop%20star%20Akon%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Shillong%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20Cherry%20Blossom%20Festival%202024%2C%20has%20said%20he%20thinks%20of%20India%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20home%26quot%3B%20and%20can%20never%20find%20himself%20in%20a%20situation%20%26quot%3Bfar%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2