%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kabir%20Bedi%20reveals%20why%20Parveen%20Babi%20left%20him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731687921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115340555%2Cimgsize-53858.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkabir-bedi-reveals-parveen-babi-left-him-because-she-was-afraid-he-would-force-her-to-seek-treatment-paranoid-minds-are-scared-of-everything%2Farticleshow%2F115340458.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115340458.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20actor%20Kabir%20Bedi%20recently%20reflected%20on%20his%20brief%20yet%20intense%20relationship%20with%20actress%20Parveen%20Babi%2C%20which%20ended%20during%20a%20difficult%20time%20in%20her%20life%20as%20she%20struggled%20with%20mental%20health%20issues.%20He%20shared%20that%20he%20had%20urged%20her%20to%20seek%20treatment%2C%20but%20she%20had%20refused%20entirely.%20Aware%20that%20her%20condition%20might%20deteriorate%20without%20help%2C%20Kabir%20explained%20that%20this%20ultimately%20led%20to%20their%20separation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkabir-bedi-reveals-parveen-babi-left-him-because-she-was-afraid-he-would-force-her-to-seek-treatment-paranoid-minds-are-scared-of-everything%2Farticleshow%2F115340458.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah's%20Big%20Praise%20As%20Cocaine%20Worth%20Rs%20900%20Crore%20Seized%20From%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2080%20kg%20of%20high-grade%20cocaine%20worth%20around%20Rs%20900%20crore%20was%20recovered%20by%20the%20anti-drugs%20agency%20in%20Delhi%20today.%20The%20seizure%20of%20the%20party%20drug%20-%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20hauls%20of%20cocaine%20in%20Delhi%26quot%3B%20-%20came%20on%20a%20day%20a%20joint%20operation%20by%20the%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%20(NCB)%2C%20Navy%20and%20Gujarat%20ATS%20led%20to%20the%20recovery%20of%20nearly%20700%20kg%20of%20Methamphetamine%20off%20the%20Gujarat%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seizures%20drew%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20praise%20who%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bbreakthroughs%26quot%3B%20reflect%20the%20government's%20resolve%20to%20build%20a%20%26quot%3Bdrug-free%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCB%20revealed%20that%20the%20confiscation%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20was%20a%20result%20of%20months%20of%20work%20on%20the%20leads%20developed%20during%20previous%20seizures%20in%20March%20and%20August.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20working%20on%20the%20leads%20generated%20during%20the%20seizures%20in%20March%20and%20August%202024%2C%20and%20through%20technical%20and%20human%20intelligence%2C%20the%20NCB%20was%20finally%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20source%20of%20the%20contraband%20and%2082.53%20kg%20of%20high-grade%20cocaine%20was%20recovered%20from%20Janakpuri%20and%20Nangloi%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20massive%20drug%20consignment%20worth%20approximately%20Rs%20900%20crore%20was%20tracked%20down%20by%20a%20bottom-to-top%20approach%20after%20drugs%20were%20seized%20in%20a%20courier%20centre%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20initially%20recovered%20drugs%20from%20a%20courier%20shop%20from%20a%20parcel%20meant%20for%20Australia.%20The%20agency%20said%20it%20was%20able%20to%20backtrack%20the%20supply%20despite%20%26quot%3Bcut-offs%20to%20the%20bulk%20quantity%2C%20which%20was%20concealed%20in%20Janakpuri%20and%20Nangloi%20areas%20of%20Delhi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20syndicate%20was%20being%20operated%20by%20a%20group%20of%20people%20based%20abroad%2C%20revealed%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20the%20accused%20were%20mainly%20%26quot%3Bhawala%20operators%20and%20anonymous%20to%20each%20other%26quot%3B.%20They%20used%20%26quot%3Bpseudo-names%20for%20day-to-day%20conversations%20on%20drug%20dealing%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20NCB%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20operatives%20of%20the%20syndicate%2C%20residents%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Sonipat%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seizure%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20after%20an%20operation%20on%20the%20sea%2C%20saw%20the%20arrest%20of%20eight%20Iranian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20operation%20codenamed%20'Sagar%20Manthan-%204'%20was%20launched%20based%20on%20intelligence%20inputs%20to%20intercept%20an%20un-registered%20vessel%2C%20without%20an%20AIS%20(automatic%20identification%20system)%20or%20an%20electronic%20boat%20or%20ship-tracking%20indicator%2C%20that%20will%20be%20entering%20the%20Indian%20waters%20with%20drugs%2C%20the%20NCB%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20congratulated%20the%20federal%20anti-narcotics%20agency%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bmajor%26quot%3B%20success%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20government's%20hunt%20against%20drug%20rackets%20will%20continue%20%26quot%3Bruthlessly%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731687900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F9p3mijm_delhi-drug-bust_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fcocaine-worth-rs-900-crore-seized-in-one-of-delhis-biggest-drug-busts-7028513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%2080%20kg%20of%20high-grade%20cocaine%20worth%20around%20Rs%20900%20crore%20was%20recovered%20by%20the%20anti-drugs%20agency%20in%20Delhi%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Most%20Advanced%20Satellite%20Launch%20From%20US%20Is%20Elon%20Musk's%20'Trump'%20Card%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESpaceX%2C%20the%20company%20owned%20by%20'The%20First%20Buddy'%20of%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20is%20the%20first%20big%20beneficiary%20of%20a%20multi-million%20dollar%20deal%20inked%20by%20India's%20space%20agency.%20Early%20next%20week%2C%20SpaceX's%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20will%20take%20India's%20most%20modern%20communications%20satellite%20GSAT-20%2C%20also%20called%20GSAT%20N-2%2C%20into%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20of%20many%20commercial%20engagements%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20has%20with%20SpaceX.%20While%20some%20say%20ISRO%20and%20SpaceX%20are%20competitors%20for%20low-cost%20launches%2C%20in%20the%20global%20commercial%20space%20market%20no%20one%20doubts%20that%20SpaceX%20is%20way-way%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20well-known%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20share%20a%20great%20bond%20with%20each%20calling%20the%20other%20%26quot%3Bmy%20friend%26quot%3B.%20The%20maverick%20entrepreneur%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20also%20friends%20with%20both%20of%20them%2C%20with%20Elon%20Musk%20saying%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20fan%20of%20Modi%26quot%3B.%20The%20optics%20and%20timing%20of%20the%20space%20launch%20are%20just%20right%2C%20but%20incidentally%20the%20deals%20predate%20the%20American%20election%20results%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20critics%20of%20either%20Washington%20DC%20or%20New%20Delhi%20cannot%20raise%20%26quot%3Bcrony%20capitalism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GSAT-N2%20will%20be%20launched%20from%20Cape%20Canaveral%20in%20the%20US.%20Made%20by%20ISRO%2C%20this%204%2C700%20kg%20satellite%20was%20too%20heavy%20for%20Indian%20rockets%20to%20carry%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-preps-us-launch-of-advanced-satellite-gsat-20-for-enabling-in-flight-internet-7026412%5C%22%3Ehence%20the%20foreign%20commercial%20launch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20India's%20own%20rocket%20'The%20Bahubali'%20or%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-3%20could%20have%20at%20best%20lifted%20a%20maximum%20of%20about%204%2C000-4%2C100%20kg%20into%20a%20geostationary%20transfer%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20till%20now%20leaned%20on%20Arianespace%20to%20launch%20its%20heavy%20satellites%2C%20but%20at%20present%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20operational%20rockets%20and%20the%20only%20reliable%20option%20India%20had%20was%20to%20go%20with%20SpaceX.%20Chinese%20rockets%20are%20a%20no-go%20for%20India%2C%20and%20Russia%20is%20not%20able%20to%20offer%20its%20rockets%20for%20commercial%20launches%20due%20to%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20a%20good%20deal%20on%20this%20maiden%20launch%20with%20SpaceX%2C%26quot%3B%20Radhakrishnan%20Durairaj%2C%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20New%20Space%20India%20Ltd%20(NSIL)%2C%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20commercial%20arm%20of%20ISRO%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20price%20for%20launching%20this%20particular%20satellite...%20the%20technical%20compatibility%20and%20also%20the%20commercial%20deals...%20I%20would%20say%20it%20was%20a%20good%20deal%20for%20us%2C%20for%20launching%20such%20a%20heavy%20satellite%20on%20SpaceX's%20Falcon%209%20rocket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvtsqvckg_elon-musk-pm-modi_650x400_10_April_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20made%20GSAT-N2%2C%20with%20a%20lift-off%20mass%20of%204%2C700%20kg%2C%20and%20has%20a%20mission%20life%20of%2014%20years.%20It%20is%20a%20purely%20commercial%20launch%20being%20front-ended%20by%20NSIL.%20The%20satellite%20is%20equipped%20with%2032%20user%20beams%2C%20comprising%20eight%20narrow%20spot%20beams%20over%20the%20northeast%20region%20and%2024%20wide%20spot%20beams%20over%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20These%2032%20beams%20will%20be%20supported%20by%20hub%20stations%20located%20within%20mainland%20India.%20It%20will%20also%20help%20enable%20in-flight%20Internet%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20and%20former%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20will%20lead%20the%20newly%20created%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20a%20fan%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20June%2021%2C%202023%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20incredibly%20excited%20about%20the%20future%20of%20India.%20India%20has%20more%20promise%20than%20any%20large%20country%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20(PM%20Modi)%20really%20cares%20about%20India%20as%20he's%20pushing%20us%20to%20make%20significant%20investments%20in%20India.%20I%20am%20a%20fan%20of%20Modi.%20It%20was%20a%20fantastic%20meeting%20and%20I%20like%20him%20quite%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20this%20single%20dedicated%20commercial%20launch%20of%20the%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20to%20lift%20India's%20communications%20satellite%20will%20cost%20%2460-70%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20the%20Tesla%20chief%20has%20been%20asking%20India%20to%20grant%20SpaceX%20licence%20to%20sell%20satellite-based%20Internet%20services%20in%20India%20using%20its%20Starlink%20Constellation.%20%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20bringing%20Starlink%20to%20India%20where%20it%20will%20help%20remote%20villages%2C%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Telecom%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20said%20Elon%20Musk-owned%20Starlink%20is%20yet%20to%20comply%20with%20security%20norms%2C%20and%20a%20licence%20for%20satellite%20communications%20services%20will%20be%20issued%20only%20after%20they%20meet%20all%20the%20requirements%20for%20services%20in%20India.%20The%20satellite%20communication%20services%20major%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20completing%20all%20the%20requirements%20and%20will%20get%20a%20licence%20once%20they%20complete%20the%20process%2C%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20give%20them%20(licence)%20if%20they%20(Starlink)%20comply%20with%20all%20the%20conditions.%20You%20have%20to%20look%20at%20it%20from%20a%20security%20perspective%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20all%20security%20concerns%20are%20addressed.%20When%20they%20do%20that%20we%20will%20be%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20give%20it.%20Obviously%2C%20they%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20inked%20another%20commercial%20deal%20with%20the%20Houston-based%20company%20Axiom%20Space%20to%20send%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20on-board%20the%20SpaceX%20Falcon%209%20and%20Crew%20Dragon%20human%20space%20flight%20system.%20That%20deal%20is%20expected%20to%20cost%20%2460%20million.%20Earnings%20by%20SpaceX%20from%20the%20mission%20to%20send%20the%20astronaut%20could%20be%20much%20lower%20as%20four%20astronauts%20are%20sharing%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731687840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F64ftumb8_pm-modi-elon-musk-reuters-650-_650x400_21_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-most-advanced-satellite-gsat-n2-launch-from-us-on-spacex-falcon-9-is-elon-musks-trump-card-7028568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpaceX%2C%20the%20company%20owned%20by%20'The%20First%20Buddy'%20of%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20is%20the%20first%20big%20beneficiary%20of%20a%20multi-million%20dollar%20deal%20inked%20by%20India's%20space%20agency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage