0build%20their%20first%20project%20step-by-step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20design%20thinking%20module%2C%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20explore%20their%20passions%20through%20exercises%20like%20the%20Ikigai%20exercise%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20find%20the%20overlap%20between%20what%20they%20love%2C%20what%20they%E2%80%99re%20good%20at%2C%20and%20what%20problems%20they%20can%20solve%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasises%20that%20LaunchPad%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20accessible%20and%20engaging.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20content%20is%20designed%20for%20teenagers%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20too%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20too%20basic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20students%20to%20feel%20like%20they%E2%80%99re%20learning%20real%2C%20practical%20skills%20that%20they%20can%20apply%20at%20their%20workplace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20early%20challenges%3A%20Launching%20the%20platform%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20platform%20like%20LaunchPad%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20without%20its%20challenges.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20hurdles%20Aryan%20faced%20was%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20get%20approval%20for%20the%20idea%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20how%20to%20spark%20interest%20among%20students%20about%20the%20website.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20pitched%20the%20idea%2C%20I%20went%20from%20class%20to%20class%2C%20speaking%20with%20students%20and%20noting%20down%20their%20names%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faced%20many%20of%20the%20same%20obstacles%20that%20any%20young%20entrepreneur%20faces%20when%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20community.%20He%20realised%20that%20in%20order%20to%20grow%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20increase%20the%20click-through%20rate%20on%20the%20website%20and%20boost%20user%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20by%20experimenting