and%20learn%20from%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20in%20our%20villages%2C%20artists%20would%20interact%20with%20each%20other%20at%20cultural%20events%20and%20weddings%2C%20where%20they%20would%20get%20to%20play%20night%20after%20night.%20But%20that%20system%20has%20ended%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20residency%20took%20place%20in%20Pokhran%2C%20with%20support%20from%20BlueCity%20Walls%2C%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20and%20some%20anonymous%20funders.%20Speaking%20with%20Rakshat%20Hooja%2C%20the%20current%20head%20of%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20%3Cem%3ERajasthani%20%3C%2Fem%3Efolk%20music%20is%20thriving%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20established%20artists%20who%20get%20booked%20for%20the%20entire%20year%20and%20travel%20extensively.%20For%20newcomers%2C%20however%2C%20breaking%20into%20that%20field%20remains%20a%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20social%20and%20cultural%20development%20of%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20provided%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20with%20valuable%20guidance%2C%20support%2C%20and%20assistance%20in%20raising%20funds%20for%20their%20initiatives.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20idea%20falls%20in%20line%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20we%20do.%20And%20it%20was%20lovely%20to%20see%20these%20senior%20artists%20come%20and%20mentor%20young%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rakshat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%3C%2Fem%3E%20welcomed%20around%2050%20children%2C%20ages%2012%20to%2018.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20number%20grew%20to%2078%2C%20which%20included%2010%20girls%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EMeghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%20community%20and%20participants%20from%20outside%20the%20traditional%20folk%20music%20communities.%20Both%20of%20these%20are%20as%20rare%20as%20a%20cool%20afternoon%20in%20Jaisalmer%20during%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%